"La configuration avancée (transports, formats, taxes) se fait dans votre "
"compte B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:417
msgid ""
"When an order is completed, the plugin automatically generates the invoice "
"via the B2Brouter API."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une commande est terminée, le plugin génère automatiquement la "
"facture via l'API B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:418
msgid ""
"B2Brouter sends the invoice to your customer using your configured transport "
"(email, Peppol, etc.)."
